ygData.messageBody:
The giant reminder string is on a named Hill Giant named Timber the Tiny. I
BELEIVE he's in West Karana, but it could be East or North too. ( I can't
remember =( ) The gaterskin sleeves is on a level 30ish mob. The runed
cowl I THINK is on a level 35ish or 40ish mob.

I'm not sure about the rest, but I hope this helps 'a little' =)

Lanadina
